  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK806">
<l>ellaikka ṇiṉṟār tuṟavār tolaiviṭattun</l>
<l>tollaikka ṇiṉṟār toṭarpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who stand within the limits (of true friendship) will not even in adversity give up the intimacy of long-standing friends.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
